  "detailed_description": "<strong>Pay Me In Colors</strong> is a 2D platformer game inspired by the classics of the past. The game is divided in 6 worlds, each one gives a different and challenging mechanic to explore, run through many levels and accept the challenge of giving the world colors again.<br><br><strong>Key features</strong>:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>40+</strong> levels.<br></li><li><strong>6 worlds</strong>, each with a different mechanic to challenge you.<br></li><li>Simple and responsive controls.<br></li><li>Compatible with controllers.</li></ul>",
